divs: Sighting Detailswalked outside, noticed bright stationary object south of my position. Maybe a mile away, very bright and big. Too low to be a star. Was not an airplane. Late dusk, very prominent.Still there at the moment, has not moved within half hour.
Summary: bright object stationary in sky, very bright. not moving, too low to be star. bright
